*.log
coverage/
# User screenshots (ad-hoc, not project assets)
image.png
screenshot*.png
# llm_wiki — 디버깅 잔여 스크린샷이 raw/ append-only invariant 와 충돌하지 않도록 차단.
# 의도적으로 raw/ 에 ingest 할 자료라면 source-id 로 rename 후 commit (e.g. 2026-04-26_xxx.png).
llm_wiki/raw/error*.png
llm_wiki/raw/screenshot*.png
.gstack/

# Playwright verification output (regenerable — script committed, screenshots not)
apps/**/.verify/
playwright-report/
test-results/
